properties.Name: MeterUsageForecast
properties.Description: A forecasted energy usage at a meter for a particular time interval as of a particular timestamp.

Columns.Name: MeterId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Meter.

Columns.Name: MeterUsageForecastTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the meter usage forecast was made.

Columns.Name: MeterUsageForecastPeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp associated with the meter usage forecast.

Columns.Name: MeterUsageForecastPeriodEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period end timestamp associated with the meter usage forecast.

Columns.Name: MeterUsageForecast
Columns.Description: The forecast usage of energy at this meter during the associated period.

Columns.Name: MeterUsageForecastUomId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Unit Of Measure.

Columns.Name: ForecastMethodTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Forecast Method Type.

Columns.Name: MeterUsageForecastNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Meter Usage Forecast.
